title: If You Lost Your V-Card On A School Bus Raise Your Hand!
description:
The Big Cheese, Cheese Wagon, Freshman Ferrari, Twinkie, or just The Yellow School Bus; whatever you call it, most of us can recall pivotal memories that took place there. Was losing your V-card one?
